data.title: Gold Star "Dock in a Box"
data.meta_description: Delivered anywhere in Ireland, Fresh prepared seafood dishes straight from the kitchen of The Long Dock, Carrigaholt. Our Famous Seafood Chowders, Award Winning Fish Pie and Imelda's Brown Bread
data.text:
Our Gold Star Dock in a Box, delivered anywhere in Ireland includes Four of Our Famous Seafood Chowder, Two of Our Award Winning Fish Pies , and A Loaf Imelda’s freshly baked bread, ready to enjoy immediately or suitable for freezing.

Your Order will be Freshly prepared, Chilled And Packaged Ready for Postage direct to your door.
